Great Price 👍🏾 Especially for the amount of food you get! We purchased 2 Combo specials and were greatly enthused as far as taste, quality and quantity. Breaking through shells for crab meat was fun and easy; our kid had considerable fun eating, as well. The potato, sausage, corn and shrimp were a great plus to the main course. The house special sauce was a great pairing and we definitely appreciate the LARGE butter garlic dip provided, too 😊 Get those napkins ready and dive in to some good seafood. The regulars ( salmon, grouper, red fish, blue fish) are always fresh and on sale; not everything is market price, as the sign says "Price Subject to Change Based on Customer's Attitude" 😂 Definitely going for Round 2 soon! 4 Stars 🌟
